Short:        Generate Boing Ball 3D objects
Author:       thellier@free.fr (Alain Thellier)
Uploader:     thellier free fr
Type:         dev/src
Version:      1.0
Requires:     OS4, PowerPC
Architecture: ppc-amigaos

DESCRIPTION 
Simple source that generate boing ball 3D object (Wawefront .OBJ format)
Generated objects can be imported/used/exported in Blender
Joined OS4 binary but can be compiled on any computer/OS
Joined boingball.mtl file containing material description
Joined boingball.obj file containing an example = 8x6 faces boing ball

PARAMETERS
usage: DoBoing filename xfaces yfaces xsubfaces ysubfaces										

filename: the file in Wawefront .OBJ format 
xfaces yfaces : count of red/white faces in this direction (usually 8 6)
xsubfaces ysubfaces : how much each red/white face is subdivided (usually 6 8)	
                                                                            
